OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773363777
OL,3,CTories call on Starmer's ethics
OL,4,Cadviser to investigate Mandelson
OL,5,C'cover-up'
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer's ethics adviser must
OL,8,Finvestigate whether he broke the
OL,9,Fministerial code in his handling of
OL,10,Fthe Peter Mandelson scandal, the
OL,11,FTories have said.
OL,13,FThe Opposition has written to
OL,14,Fstandards watchdog Sir Laurie Magnus
OL,15,Fcalling for him to investigate a
OL,16,F"potential cover-up" after the
OL,17,FGovernment's release of files relating
OL,18,Fto the peer becoming US ambassador.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773363777
OL,3,CTories call on Starmer's ethics
OL,4,Cadviser to investigate Mandelson
OL,5,C'cover-up'
OL,7,FDetails of his appointment and
OL,8,Fsubsequent removal from the Washington
OL,9,Fjob were disclosed in documents
OL,10,Fpublished on Wednesday in response to
OL,11,Fa "humble address" motion ` a rarely
OL,12,Fused parliamentary manoeuvre that
OL,13,Fcompels the Government to act.
OL,15,FSenior officials had concerns about
OL,16,FLord Mandelson taking up the role and
OL,17,Fthe Prime Minister was warned there
OL,18,Fwas a "general reputational risk" over
OL,19,Fthe peer's relationship with
OL,20,Fpaedophile Jeffrey Epstein, the papers
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,26,@sD@COUsD@RO]zD@GOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773363777
OL,3,CTories call on Starmer's ethics
OL,4,Cadviser to investigate Mandelson
OL,5,C'cover-up'
OL,7,FBut in a letter to Sir Laurie, shadow
OL,8,FCabinet Office minister Alex Burghart
OL,9,Fsuggested there was "missing"
OL,10,Fcorrespondence in the published
OL,11,Fmaterial, and that complying only
OL,12,Fpartially with the demand by MPs may
OL,13,Fbe a contempt of Parliament.
OL,15,F"There is no document disclosing
OL,16,Fwhether these reservations were
OL,17,Fcommunicated to the Prime Minister,"
OL,18,Fhe said.
OL,26,@qD@UOUqD@]O]wD@AOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773363777
OL,3,CTories call on Starmer's ethics
OL,4,Cadviser to investigate Mandelson
OL,5,C'cover-up'
OL,7,FMr Burghart also questioned why
OL,8,Fpublished files relating to a fact-
OL,9,Ffinding process surrounding Lord
OL,10,FMandelson's dismissal did not include
OL,11,Fdiscussions with figures like then-No
OL,12,F10 chief of staff Morgan McSweeney or
OL,13,Fthe Prime Minister himself.
OL,15,F"Either further records exist and have
OL,16,Fbeen withheld, or the investigation
OL,17,Fwas woefully inadequate," the
OL,18,FConservative frontbencher said.
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773363777
OL,3,CTories call on Starmer's ethics
OL,4,Cadviser to investigate Mandelson
OL,5,C'cover-up'
OL,7,FA Labour source dismissed the Tory
OL,8,Fsuggestions as "conspiratorial
OL,9,Fnonsense" while the Government
OL,10,Freiterated that it was committed to
OL,11,Fcomplying in full with the humble
OL,12,Faddress.
OL,14,FThe 31 files released on Wednesday did
OL,15,Fnot include correspondence between No
OL,16,F10 and Lord Mandelson, in which a
OL,17,Fnumber of follow-up questions were
OL,18,Fasked about his relationship with
OL,19,FEpstein.
OL,26,@pD@POUqD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773363777
OL,3,CTories call on Starmer's ethics
OL,4,Cadviser to investigate Mandelson
OL,5,C'cover-up'
OL,7,FMPs have been told those exchanges
OL,8,Fremained subject to the Metropolitan
OL,9,FPolice's ongoing investigation into
OL,10,Fthe peer over allegations of
OL,11,Fmisconduct in public office.
OL,13,FBut Mr Burghart's letter also asks
OL,14,Fwhether Sir Keir misled Parliament by
OL,15,Fsaying he would not have appointed
OL,16,FLord Mandelson had he known the full
OL,17,Fextent of his association with Epstein
OL,18,F` a claim which it says is
OL,19,F"irreconcilable" with information laid
OL,20,Fbare in the files.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773363777
OL,3,CTories call on Starmer's ethics
OL,4,Cadviser to investigate Mandelson
OL,5,C'cover-up'
OL,7,F"The documents published on 11 March
OL,8,F2026 raise serious questions.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773363777
OL,3,CTories call on Starmer's ethics
OL,4,Cadviser to investigate Mandelson
OL,5,C'cover-up'
OL,7,F"They demonstrate that: the Prime
OL,8,FMinister was warned of the risks of
OL,9,Fappointing Lord Mandelson and
OL,10,Fproceeded regardless; his own national
OL,11,Fsecurity adviser described the process
OL,12,Fas 'weirdly rushed'; his assurance to
OL,13,Fthe House that 'full due process was
OL,14,Ffollowed' was not an accurate
OL,15,Frepresentation of events; and his
OL,16,Fsubsequent claim that he would not
OL,17,Fhave made the appointment had he known
OL,18,Fthe facts is contradicted by the due
OL,19,Fdiligence document he himself
OL,20,Freviewed," Mr Burghart wrote.
OL,26,@oD@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773363777
OL,3,CTories call on Starmer's ethics
OL,4,Cadviser to investigate Mandelson
OL,5,C'cover-up'
OL,7,F"I therefore ask you to undertake an
OL,8,Finvestigation into whether the Prime
OL,9,FMinister has broken the ministerial
OL,10,Fcode."
OL,12,FEarlier on Thursday, Sir Keir took
OL,13,Fresponsibility for the "mistake" of
OL,14,Fappointing the peer, but Downing
OL,15,FStreet denied suggestions of a "cover-
OL,16,Fup" and said that no notes by the
OL,17,FPrime Minister were redacted.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@FO]uD@XOUuD@`O]wD@`OUxD@CO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773363777
OL,3,CTories call on Starmer's ethics
OL,4,Cadviser to investigate Mandelson
OL,5,C'cover-up'
OL,7,F"There are a range of different ways
OL,8,Fin which the Prime Minister's senior
OL,9,Fteam responds to advice," his official
OL,10,Fspokesman said.
OL,12,FHe added: "The Prime Minister did read
OL,13,Fthe advice, but clearly there are
OL,14,Flessons to be learned on the wider
OL,15,Fappointment processes, and the
OL,16,Fprocesses that led up to them."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@YO]tD@KOUxD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
