PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773363777
OL,3,CTories call on Starmer's ethics
OL,4,Cadviser to investigate Mandelson
OL,5,C'cover-up'
OL,7,FSome files which touch on national
OL,8,Fsecurity or foreign relations matters
OL,9,Fwill be redacted but the final say on
OL,10,Fthat rests with Parliament's
OL,11,FIntelligence and Security Committee.
OL,13,FJust one of the documents released on
OL,14,FWednesday was redacted in agreement
OL,15,Fwith the committee.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773363777
OL,3,CTories call on Starmer's ethics
OL,4,Cadviser to investigate Mandelson
OL,5,C'cover-up'
OL,7,FThe Government has also agreed a
OL,8,Fframework with the Metropolitan Police
OL,9,Fon which documents can be released
OL,10,Fwithout prejudicing the ongoing
OL,11,Finvestigation into the former
OL,12,Fambassador.
OL,14,FLord Mandelson was arrested on
OL,15,FFebruary 23 on suspicion of misconduct
OL,16,Fin public office, having been accused
OL,17,Fof passing sensitive information on to
OL,18,FEpstein during his time as business
OL,19,Fsecretary in Gordon Brown's government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773363777
OL,3,CTories call on Starmer's ethics
OL,4,Cadviser to investigate Mandelson
OL,5,C'cover-up'
OL,7,FHe was subsequently bailed, but later
OL,8,Freleased from his bail conditions,
OL,9,Falthough he remains under
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,FA Government spokesman said: "The
OL,13,FGovernment is committed to complying
OL,14,Fwith the humble address in full, while
OL,15,Fcontinuing to support the Metropolitan
OL,16,FPolice in their investigation."
OL,26,@tD@^OUxD@_O]
